   Rickey is survived by sons Stuart, a documentary filmmaker in San
Francisco, and Philip, a sculptor and landscape designer in St. Paul;
and two grandchildren.

   This is part of a federal effort to upgrade the nation's four
firefighting air guard units. The others are in Cheyenne, Wyo.;
